data.description: LOWEST PRICE 5/BED 3/BATH IN COMMUNITY! NO CDD & LOW HOA fees makes this home the PERFECT INVESTMENT! With a Bedroom and Full Bathroom on Main Level-This well-appointed 5/Bedroom home in the sought after Del Tierra neighborhood is situated on a Corner Lot on a Beautiful Lake, offering privacy and wildlife views! As you pass your front covered porch with upgraded Plank Tile flooring and decorative ceiling it is the perfect spot to sit and watch the spectacular sunsets! Step inside the foyer with the dining room to the right with upgraded chandelier and a little further is an Open Floor plan with the kitchen/family room combo.  The kitchen offers Granite Counter-tops and a large center island, perfect for family gatherings & entertaining.  An upgraded large single sink & facet, with a decorative backsplash complimenting the cabinet colors and decorative pendant lights adorn the kitchen space.  There is a Bedroom on the 1st floor-perfect for guest or can serve as an in-law suite, with a full Bathroom across the hall.  Venture upstairs to the Master Suite and additional four Bedrooms.  The sizable Loft space upstairs is perfect for a second den area for the family to hang out.  The large Master has double windows bringing in plenty of light, walk in closets and the Master Bath offers dual vanity and a walk-in shower.  The other three Bedrooms share a hallway Bathroom with dual vanity and the laundry room is upstairs for convenience.  The Lanai space is open looking out to the vast yard and there is plenty of room for a pool.  This community is Lakewood Ranch elementary & middle schools and the New State-of-the-Art High School Parrish Community with the bus pick up across the street.  The amenities include a Zero-entry Resort Style Pool, Fitness Center, Soccer Field, Playground and walking distance from the property location.  For an Investment it can rent out 6 month minimum and only $100/month for the HOA with NO CDD Fees!  With tons of nearby Shopping & Dining choices and UTC Mall approx. 15 minutes away and beaches nearby this is the perfect Florida Lifestyle for Working, Playing & Soaking up the Amazing Sunshine! #NOCDD #LOWHOA
